  "keyFeatures": [
    "Safe module for automated fee collection on CoW Protocol",
    "Multi-chain support (Ethereum, Gnosis, Arbitrum, Base, etc.)",
    "CLI keeper tool for automated token swapping to native tokens",
    "Configurable token filtering and minimum output thresholds",
    "Multiple token discovery strategies (explorer API or on-chain events)",
    "Batch order placement with configurable slippage",
    "Permission-controlled operations (keeper-only access)"
